snippet.title: NodeJS REST API: Super Simple Setup - Express & NPM (Ep1)
snippet.description:
Setting up a nodejs server is extremely easy nowadays using NPM.  In today's lesson, I'll show you how to get up and running in no time. By the end of this video you'll have a little server that allows you to return some JSON objects.
